name: composite_bmwm
jaxpr:
{ lambda ; a:f32[12,4]. let
    b:f32[12,4] = custom_jvp_call[
      name=relu
      call_jaxpr={ lambda ; c:f32[12,4]. let
          d:f32[12,4] = jit[
            name=relu
            jaxpr={ lambda ; c:f32[12,4]. let
                d:f32[12,4] = max c 0.0:f32[]
              in (d,) }
          ] c
        in (d,) }
      jvp=jvp
      symbolic_zeros=False
    ] a
    e:f32[12,4] = abs a
    f:f32[12,4] = neg e
    g:f32[12,4] = exp f
    h:f32[12,4] = add b g
    i:f32[12,4] = sin a
    j:f32[12,4] = add h i
  in (j,) }
